<p>“Over the past six years, we’ve worked with over 250 industry leaders to develop an unmatched learning experience, and have trained over 50,000 professionals in our campuses in New York, Toronto, and Vancouver. With Online Live learning, we have combined proven instructor-led, collaborative learning with the convenience of an online experience, to really provide an engaging, effective alternative to ‘learn at your own pace’ learning models,” said Jason Field, our Founder and CEO,  <a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2018/05/prweb15513469.htm">in a press release</a>:</p>
<p>Check out this video to take a look at Online Live learning in action:</p>
